@Refit_Demo_Host = http://127.0.0.1:5235
@token = 

### 1. 登录拿 JWT
POST {{Refit_Demo_Host}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 2. Refit：列表（Query）
GET {{Refit_Demo_Host}}/refit-demo/todos?completed=false&limit=10

### 3. Refit：单条（Task&lt;T&gt; / ApiException）
GET {{Refit_Demo_Host}}/refit-demo/todos/1

### 4. Refit：单条安全读（IApiResponse，故意 404）
GET {{Refit_Demo_Host}}/refit-demo/todos/999/safe

### 5. Refit：创建（Body）
POST {{Refit_Demo_Host}}/refit-demo/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Created via Refit",
  "completed": false
}

### 6. Refit + Auth Handler 转发 JWT（先把上面 login 返回的 token 填到 @token）
GET {{Refit_Demo_Host}}/refit-demo/todos/secure/mine
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
